data.description: * MOTIVATED SELLER * Will entertain all reasonable offers. Welcome to your dream equestrian property! Nestled on a serene one-acre lot, this charming three-bedroom, two-bathroom home offers the perfect combination of comfortable living and horse, goat or even cow capabilities. With ample space for your beloved horses, this property is a true paradise. The three bedrooms provide excellent space for rest and relaxation, accommodating your family's needs effortlessly.  Enjoy the convenience of two well-appointed bathrooms, featuring modern fixtures and finishes. The heart of the home is a welcoming open-concept living area, perfect for entertaining friends and family and the well-equipped kitchen boasts modern appliances, ample cabinetry, and a convenient breakfast bar, making meal preparation a breeze. Large windows throughout the home fill the space with an abundance of natural light, creating a bright and airy ambiance. Enjoy your morning coffee or evening drink on the brand new, beautiful deck. A 50 amp electric hookup for a RV is already in place and the entire acre is fenced with three access gates. High speed internet is available in the area for those working from home! Owners currently have 200Mbps but up to 300 Mbps is available via Rock Solid. Starlink high speed internet is also available in the neighborhood. This peaceful and custom built property will not last! Must see the home in person to truly appreciate all the well thought out features. Schedule your private tour today!
